                            container size                     classes for fetch this media query
extra large >=1200px    ---> 1140px                               col-xl 
  large >=992px            ---> 960px                              col-lg
  medium >=768px            ---> 720px                              col-md
  small >=576px                 ---> 540px                           col-sm
  extra small < 576px              ---> auto                          no claass
